# Tech Stack

This document **locks the technology choices** for the project.

AI agents must not deviate from this stack.

---

## Frontend

- React
- Vite
- JavaScript (no TypeScript unless approved)

---

## Backend / Data

- Firebase
- Firestore (NoSQL)

---

## Hosting (Future)

- Firebase Hosting or equivalent
- No custom servers

---

## Tooling

- Node.js (LTS)
- npm
- Anti-gravity IDE
- Stitch agent loop

---

## Prohibited Tools

- Next.js
- Redux
- GraphQL
- Docker
- Kubernetes
- Experimental frameworks

---

## Stack Changes

Stack changes require:
- Clear justification
- Updated documentation
- Explicit approval
